'''彼得·尼加德'''（{{lang-sv|Peter Nygård}}, {{bd|1941年|7月24日||}}）<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kostiainen |first1=Auvo |title=Nygård, Peter |url=https://kansallisbiografia.fi/kansallisbiografia/henkilo/1 |website=kansallisbiografia.fi |publisher=Kansallisbiografia-verkkojulkaisu |accessdate=16 May 2020 |archive-date=16 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216115323/https://kansallisbiografia.fi/kansallisbiografia/henkilo/1 |url-status=live }}</ref>是一位芬兰裔加拿大企业家。

==生平==
[[File:Nicole_Midwin_with_Peter_Nygard.jpg|thumb]]出席慈善晚宴]]
[[File:Nygard_family.jpg|thumb]]
1941年出生于[[芬兰|芬兰]][[赫尔辛基|赫尔辛基]]，1952年随父母移民[[加拿大|加拿大]]。1964年毕业于[[北达科他大学|北达科他大学]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/amp/articles/fashion-mogul-peter-nygard-business-properties-to-be-sold-11588276020|title=Fashion Mogul Peter Nygard Business Properties to Be Sold|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=30 April 2020|accessdate=15 December 2020|archive-date=2 June 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200602092649/https://www.wsj.com/amp/articles/fashion-mogul-peter-nygard-business-properties-to-be-sold-11588276020|url-status=live}}</ref>1967年在[[温尼伯|温尼伯]]创建时尚服装公司[[尼加德国际|尼加德国际]]。

因[[尼加德国际|尼加德国际]]集团总部因被指控[[性贩卖|性贩卖]]，2020年2月25日卸任董事长一职。同年3月18日公司申请破产。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Fitz-Gibbon |first1=Jorge |title=Fashion mogul Peter Nygard resigns from company amid sex-trafficking accusations |url=https://www.foxnews.com/lifestyle/fashion-peter-nygard-resigns-company-accusations |website=Fox News |date=26 February 2020 |access-date=15 December 2020 |archive-date=18 August 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200818005500/https://www.foxnews.com/lifestyle/fashion-peter-nygard-resigns-company-accusations |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Johnson |first1=Kevin |title=Canadian fashion magnate Peter Nygard charged in sex trafficking scheme, including minors |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/12/15/fashion-mogul-peter-nygard-charged-sex-trafficking-women-and-girls/3908214001/ |website=USA TODAY |access-date=2020-12-20 |archive-date=2021-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211022185608/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/2020/12/15/fashion-mogul-peter-nygard-charged-sex-trafficking-women-and-girls/3908214001/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cnwtelbec.com/en/releases/archive/September2007/30/c6818.html?view=print |title=$26.5 million Raised Nationwide as Canadian Breast Cancer Foundation CIBC Run for the Cure Celebrates Sweet Sixteen |publisher=Cnwtelbec.com |accessdate=2010-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708171234/http://www.cnwtelbec.com/en/releases/archive/September2007/30/c6818.html?view=print |archive-date=2011-07-08 |url-status=dead }}</ref>

